<c74object name='sp.smear~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Send incoming audio to mutilple outputs based on amplitude
</digest>
    <description>Send incoming audio to mutilple outputs based on amplitude.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.smear~</o> object takes audio input and runs it through an envelope follower (<o>sp.envelope~</o>). Based on the output of that it is smeared across a multi-channel output so that different amplitudes can be sent to different places.
</discussion>

